{"type": "article", "id": 59341, "title": "新年将至，为自己选一款特别的日历吧｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2018-12-15T22:56:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55123, "name": "Relative Goods"}, {"id": 54938, "name": "Poketo"}, {"id": 55124, "name": "Matthew Hoffman"}, {"id": 55125, "name": "Eloise Iturbe"}, {"id": 55126, "name": "Verlag Hermann Schmidt Mainz"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 194, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181215232302c6F5pQ10xuhPzsoE.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626; min-height: 13.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 18.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 16.0px Times; color: #343434; -webkit-text-stroke: #343434; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 19.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 28.0px; font: 24.0px Times; color: #1f1f1f; -webkit-text-stroke: #1f1f1f; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 29.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>新年将至，你准备好新一年的日历了吗？这个周末，我们准备了一组创意奇趣的日历，希望能够帮助你标记生活，记录成长，一起来看看。</p><h3>Typodarium 2019 </h3><p>自 2009 年开始，德国的 Verlag Hermann Schmidt Mainz 每年都会发布一本汇集全世界各地字体的日历，吸引了一大批忠实字体粉。</p><p>今年，他们同样从上百款字体中整理编辑出了 2019 年的日历。每个月份是一种页面颜色，放在那里好似一道彩虹。每一页的正面，是字体的展示，背面则是关于这个字体的设计、灵感和故事，所以这同时也是一本关于 365个字体故事的日历。售价 19.80 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.slanted.de/en/product/typodarium-2019-preorder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232349gt6wz8iUk1s30cMX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.353519\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232349rHCxbsW2hQRdZej6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232350KJ2d5XQ8vOWgSVEa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232350dy7ix2MZ9sveBcNC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232349b9QsVcD5tLNHIJZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812152323510u8bJrDEvnpV5A7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232351ZDoQR9fXGuynkTzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2019 Wall Art Calendar by Eloise Iturbe for Poketo </h3><p>这个引人注目的日历由阿根廷艺术家Eloise Iturbe设计。</p><p>她对色彩、纹理、纸张、木材、植物和阳光十分热爱，于是将这两个世界融合在一起，组成一系列自然极简而丰富、多彩整洁，富有动感、优雅俏皮的图像，日历的每个月都有不同的色彩照亮美丽的现代艺术品，让需要美感的空间充满活力。售价 32 美元，<a href=\"https://www.poketo.com/products/2019-wall-art-calendar?variant=9130067591220\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232439MSWsyZHF8vu63790.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232440z25wbCUGZ01M3mfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232440Lml0ZNO18TYsAKw6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232440iDJHYZqIOVFcuBG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232440o7bSRVxFngZs5ifj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232441pcernM4fhuWb3sdV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232441trl26uksRM4bUDBK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232440O59xEaXPr42jvh1R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2019 Isometric Calendar by Relative Goods </h3><p>在接下来一年的 12 个月里，当地球 365 次围绕太阳公转，我们也将邂逅超过 3100 万秒的时间。</p><p>Relative Goods这款敢自称为“永恒”的日历，就运用了经典的设计元素，将独一无二的瞬间洞察通过十几种扭曲、超现实的几何图形随机随机组合在一起。这些视觉错差也可以带给我们无尽、永恒的冥想。哲学意味十足。售价 22 美元，<a href=\"https://relativegoods.com/products/isometric-calendar\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，首单还有 85 折优惠。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232643QRxYeDoaw9AXjIFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232643tWckAuwX4ZTUQCeM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232643ykYgre1WIfED6Htd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232644ALofY31gjWuRD5Es.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232644C4D7rB5Ox9qiFdN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DodeCal 2019 </h3><p>日历 DodeCal 每年都在出。今年 DodeCal 的这款木质多面体日历，取材于高品质的英国橡木，通过精确的数学加工呈现出标准的十二面体，十二面体的每一面都刻有一个月份的日历。</p><p>而今年的特别之处就在于，每个多面体可相互组合在一起，凹出不同的艺术造型，兼具功能性和现代美感。售价 79 英镑，<a href=\"http://dodecal.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121523281768HUwlxRcYzG2deA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232817dmbZxKT5GOzUW8Vr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812152328179bhHxG6zSF0tqsjD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232818fhrewyjPzYMR9dDI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232818UR5DLBTSwoHC2KNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232818oxaNuGnhy4kFlSjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Today - 2019 Daily Calendar by Matthew Hoffman</h3><p>这套由 Matthew Hoffman 打造的日历十分小巧可爱，跟一般的日历不同，这套名为 Today 的日历就像一叠名片，每张日历上除了年月日，还有着一些感想、趣事和鼓舞人心的短句。售价 36.5 美元，<a href=\"https://you-are-beautiful.com/collections/all/products/today-daily-calendar\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232850y1TKwSb5oC46aMXu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232850QPNWbeBrFhaGx3mt.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232850JX9h7cCIbmv2Bw4z.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232850OFetBrDMSWgQok2Z.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181215232850wYHGLW2rnzifTol6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}